<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to GameDin!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #4a5568;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .feature {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feature h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .social-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      color: #4f46e5;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to GameDin!</h1>
      <p>Your journey begins now</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= username %>,</h2>
      
      <p>We're thrilled to welcome you to GameDin! Your account has been successfully created and you're now part of our growing community of gamers and creators.</p>
      
      <p>Here's what you can do next:</p>
      
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>üéÆ Play Games</h3>
          <p>Discover and play amazing games created by our community of developers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>üé® Create</h3>
          <p>Build and share your own game experiences with our powerful tools.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>ü§ù Connect</h3>
          <p>Join communities, make friends, and collaborate with other gamers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>üèÜ Earn</h3>
          <p>Monetize your creations and earn rewards for your contributions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/dashboard" class="cta-button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:support@gamedin.gg">support@gamedin.gg</a>.</p>
      
      <p>Happy gaming!</p>
      <p><strong>The GameDin Team</strong></p>
      
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/gamedin" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/gamedin" class="social-link">Discord</a>
        <a href="https://youtube.com/gamedin" class="social-link">YouTube</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> GameDin. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/privacy" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none;">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="<%= appUrl %>/terms" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none;">Terms of Service</a>
      </p>
      <p>Don't want to receive these emails? <a href="<%= appUrl %>/settings/notifications" style="color: #4f46e5;">Update your preferences</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
